{"tid":990982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"的士司機遭警箍頸被裁不合法被殺　涉事警入稟高院促撤死因庭判決","createTime":"2019-01-22T04:48:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T18:15:30.000Z","uid":6497,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"704ee480a14e844aea8f1c9bc8df3a63023ebb48","tid":990982,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T04:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190122/s00001/86090168a671e2c85a8b9dfbdae5d5b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190122%2Fs00001%2F86090168a671e2c85a8b9dfbdae5d5b3.jpg&h=e5c7de40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警員6年前拘捕一名的士司機時，疑使用過分武力將司機制服及押上警車，司機最終全身癱瘓臥牀近一個月後不治。死因庭的陪審團早前以3比2裁定司機死於不合法被殺，即同意涉箍頸警員誤殺司機。涉案警員入稟高等法院申請司法覆核，要求撤銷死因庭的判決。<br />\n<br />\n根據入稟狀，申請人為警員林偉榮，答辯人為死因庭。申請人質疑，死因庭處理事實上出錯；在邏輯和推論方面有缺陷；相關決定的證據不足，或有事實上的錯誤；相關程序亦不恰當。<br />\n<br />\n申請人要求法庭撤銷死因庭的判決；再次就死者陳輝旺（終年65歲）展開聆訊；以及是次覆核有結果前，禁止律政司採取任何進一步的檢控行動。"},{"pid":"d805c57b576d31da725c9afe0822b5c7ed93dfbb","tid":990982,"uid":43046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T04:57:39.000Z","msg":"Nice"},{"pid":"11387ead5a9b306e83c63a484618fd26c22cc4a0","tid":990982,"uid":224952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:02:25.000Z","msg":"殺完人仲想唔認？<br />\n你估真係審死官呀"},{"pid":"c0e0737ed027dd5d247ded8bcba428952f509173","tid":990982,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:06:12.000Z","msg":"殺完人仲厚顏無恥到佢呢<br />\n<br />\n鄭若華條八婆又唔落 charge ?"},{"pid":"fd0ffd88df5a33327be70caddd62470f17cccbc0","tid":990982,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0e0737ed027dd5d247ded8bcba428952f509173","tid":990982,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:06:12.000Z","msg":"殺完人仲厚顏無恥到佢呢<br />\n<br />\n鄭若華條八婆又唔落 charge ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:29:58.000Z","msg":"你地冇做錯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39b82f00b94d1ebfe142d30b6f46cfc49b8ac8c","tid":990982,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:44:20.000Z","msg":"其實係監生扭斷頸"},{"pid":"a366d451e720a3315ab4cc902ef31bcc37c38623","tid":990982,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:45:13.000Z","msg":"高層今日有無震怒？"},{"pid":"1687cc9a67f00c6af2997b7b72b5c5be5a659cd4","tid":990982,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:45:21.000Z","msg":"個狗樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4492ca7d1cd8d1e0904ff07d31c5ef23140eb376","tid":990982,"uid":202278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T18:15:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}